Author: Imad El Badisy [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Imad El Badisy <elbadisyimad@gmail.com>
Description: Functional machine learning toolkit with a formula-first interface.
    Provides thin S3 wrappers around base learners and popular engines using
    functional composition via the functionals package. Includes evaluation,
    tuning, and interpretability utilities with ggplot2 visualizations.
